'''Montfort''' ([[Limburgtongo|Limburgt.]]: ''Mofert'') ben wan presi ini a minti [[Roerdalen|Roerdalen]] (bakaseywan [[Ambt Montfort|Ambt Montfort]]) ini [[Limburgkondre|Limburgkondre]], taki ofisali wan provinsi fu [[Bakratongo|Bakratongo]] ben leki a nen [[Limburg (Bakratongo)|Limburg]].

A [[Presiplusplus|presiplusplus]] ben [[Montfort (presi)|Montfort]]. Trawan funen presi ben [[Aan de Berg|Aan de Berg]], [[Eikenwal|Eikenwal]] nanga a [[Rozendaal|Rozendaal]].

A presi abi {{stow enki}} [[Km²|km²]], pefu {{stow enki}} km² watra, leki flaku nanga 4.000 (foswan mun 2008) man ini sin taki wan spredi gi fu {{stow enki}} man ies km².

A net-teki ben 0475 nanga a postukode ben 6065. Funen autorustaru ben a A73.

== Turism ==
Montfort e ben noni fu si kasteli, [[Ruini Montfort|Ruini Montfort]]. Leki a nen e taki, disi kasteli e ben wan ruini. Ini a bigin fu a 21-100-yari o bigin man nanga a rikonstruksi fu a yagtituri (''jachtoeare'') Disi turi lunga foswan no nanga a kasteli, ma ben abra [[1800|1800]] da nanga e bu. A kasteli e ben a trugupisi numro wan fu Montfort.

== Tongo ==
Man taki wan [[Limburgtongo|Limburgtongo]] dialekti basi opo wan [[Belgikondre|Belgikondre]] varianti e nen a [[Montforttongo|Montforttongo]] (''Mofers'') Disi [[Tongo|tongo]] e abi wan fu spesyal tengi, ''gäötje'' fu pikinwortu fu ''gaat'' (trawan tongo taki fu ''gaetje'') nanga wan ''luiterke'' (a pikinwortu fu ''gaot'' efru ''luiter''). 

A presi e abi wan stopulakidenki fu a delibaka ini a 19-100-yari.

